{"tid":1351364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喂喂喂cctvb你唔好諗住咁樣播足元朗堆片單野就洗到底wo","createTime":"2019-07-22T15:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T15:41:40.000Z","uid":35365,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f6fcd76e474b07d8b4b4434ef7e1d3571d163856","tid":1351364,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:16:59.000Z","msg":"屋企要睇cctvb咁啱睇到晚間新聞<br />\n竟然一開波頭15分鐘focus晒落元朗單野<br />\n播晒柳爺林卓廷爆缸流血<br />\n後生仔遞完眼鏡畀人一搥打飛<br />\n游乃海阿哥9up搵唔到攻擊性武器但配片白衫揸鐵通同阿蛇一齊行<br />\n利君雅追住淋奠盧狗狂屌<br />\n<br />\ncctvb咁好死有d唔正常<br />\n懷疑開始落order塑造鄉黑暴徒形象<br />\n然後黑警遲下扮下野做野拉人<br />\n諗住咁樣黎挽回民望<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw 2145中間個轉新聞仲係完全冇提過元朗事件<br />\n淨係播中聯辦條撚屌鳩up個段<br />\n記住cctvb點都唔會係好人<br />\n但作為黨台既cctvb<br />\n佢地既報導方法或者可以參透到對家下一步想玩咩"},{"pid":"cb932efc08de17d35de489dcb7ebc2fe6eedc9cd","tid":1351364,"uid":199709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:19:51.000Z","msg":"<strong>上環Video 整合 (粗略) (keep updating) </strong> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1348465/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1348465/page/1</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1348232/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1348232/page/1</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1346116/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1346116/page/1</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1348209/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1348209/page/1</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1350647/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1350647/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n(最新片段) 尋晚警犬無舉旗下連開四槍以上 <a href=\"https://vimeo.com/349470836\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F349470836&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=ae3ad8df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/349470836</a><br />\n721 上環發生了什麼事？ <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=2&amp;v=2bX6CKzg_5w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D2%26v%3D2bX6CKzg_5w&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=e3e924a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=2&amp;v=2bX6CKzg_5w</a><br />\n【721回顧 | 警察先主動進攻 狂射催淚彈橡膠彈】 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=341910530087022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D341910530087022&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=2c99cfb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=341910530087022</a><br />\n23:34 於永安中心外，示威者呼籲全部人「一齊走」。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D347322312837536&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=19b72720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:44 警察向示威者開槍。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D336543320631999&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=cb4719b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999</a><br />\n【721即時】22:38 在示威者推進途中，警方突然向人群射出催淚彈，及急速推進。示威者向警方投擲雜物還擊，警方再發射多枚催淚彈。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D436610810398685&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=87d92b06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:12 港澳碼頭外，警察向示威者施放胡椒噴霧。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D497139927720468&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=cf6f1dc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:00 干諾道西港澳碼頭外警察突然推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2450364665024731&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=ac771f3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731</a><br />\n21:20 警察以「一二一二」的口令由德輔道西向西邊街推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1310939165740421&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=ecf0eac8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421</a><br />\n20:55 中區警署外的示威者向警署外牆掉油漆彈、磚頭及腐蝕性液體 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D725595331211578&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=8a8319d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578</a><br />\n20:23 有一批全black bloc的警員不斷推進防線，惟沒有委任證及證明文件。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D406909290170265&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=d337c642\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265</a><br />\n20:13 示威者現正由干諾道西向後奔跑至德輔道西。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D789204521474060&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=cd4af1c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060</a><br />\n <br />\n上環清場中 警方對這個用身體阻擋催淚彈的男人這樣處理 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAzZoteAvCyw&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=175437ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw</a><br />\n示威者疑中槍倒地 同伴築防線助急救 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2433207320290299&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=57bbe2c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299</a><br />\n2019/0721/上環硝煙花特別多 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBpfKm3Ls34U%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=290e951b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n2019/07/21上環。抗爭者心聲。他們有不想活的覺悟。 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4OKmzwmhIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DS4OKmzwmhIo&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=bdc7c332\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4OKmzwmhIo</a><br />\n黑警用橡膠子彈射頭 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F2433207320290299%2F&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=0caf17d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299/</a><br />\n[上環 7.21] 蘋果影到有義士訓低咗，綠衫圍著 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ApplePhotographers/photos/a.1131233677080155/1131269430409913?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%