5204017598/</a><br />\n【7.21 現場】警察防線前的媽媽 Stand News 立場新聞 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/679125395894103/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F679125395894103%2F&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=8aeb5e52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/679125395894103/</a><br />\n【721開槍實錄】 克警濫暴，我們必定會追究到底。 林鄭，請爲每滴港人流的血負責。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/godblesshk/videos/583308962199292/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgodblesshk%2Fvideos%2F583308962199292%2F&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=f2ccdd30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/godblesshk/videos/583308962199292/</a><br />\n2019.07.21【中聯辦外示威者發表宣言】斥政府冷漠面對民間訴求 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VDZ6SZIliQA&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVDZ6SZIliQA%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=61b71b8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VDZ6SZIliQA&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n20190721 10:59 臨時街停車場 對出 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EgF3afU7NSY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEgF3afU7NSY&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=64559523\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EgF3afU7NSY</a><br />\n20190721 10:20PM 信德中心 天橋 對出 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KSn1vhTunl8&amp;t=7s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKSn1vhTunl8%26t%3D7s&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=4d32bee3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KSn1vhTunl8&amp;t=7s</a><br />\n警方在上環驅散示威者 多次施放催淚彈和發射橡膠子彈 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VKI-jSfhiO0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r