t=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/sebe2fkq</a> <br />\n(7.21)(23.24)示威者疑中槍倒地 同伴築防線助急救 <br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/pmg9i1vt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fpmg9i1vt&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=7d863005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/pmg9i1vt</a> <br />\n(7.21)（23:10）有示威者站在警方防線前，在沒有作出任何攻擊下突然被警察拉走，警察更阻止記者上前拍攝。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/xkkjcdf1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fxkkjcdf1&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=fae12fbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/xkkjcdf1</a> <br />\n(721)警方施放催淚彈後，現場煙霧瀰漫，防暴警察更在濃煙中用警棍毆打示威者。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/nq6ia5ue\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fnq6ia5ue&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=689659f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/nq6ia5ue</a>"},{"pid":"9ea64065e1ee836bf7ff9405bd27b4cf1bd1434a","tid":1351364,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:20:57.000Z","msg":"何君妖申請緊做美國人，快啲入嚟簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢做咗噤多野，一定要享受大灣區嘅榮耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/make-junius-ho-kwan-yiu-and-his-immediate-family-members-ineligible-us-entry-citizenship-and-visas\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fmake-junius-ho-kwan-yiu-and-his-immediate-family-members-ineligible-us-entry-citizenship-and-visas&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=5b252b17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/make-junius-ho-kwan-yiu-and-his-immediate-family-members-ineligible-us-entry-citizenship-and-vi