疑中槍倒地 同伴築防線助急救 <br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/pmg9i1vt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fpmg9i1vt&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=7d863005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/pmg9i1vt</a> <br />\n(7.21)（23:10）有示威者站在警方防線前，在沒有作出任何攻擊下突然被警察拉走，警察更阻止記者上前拍攝。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/xkkjcdf1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fxkkjcdf1&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=fae12fbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/xkkjcdf1</a> <br />\n(721)警方施放催淚彈後，現場煙霧瀰漫，防暴警察更在濃煙中用警棍毆打示威者。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/nq6ia5ue\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fnq6ia5ue&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn26bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=689659f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/nq6ia5ue</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:22:52.000Z","msg":"上環元朗兩邊發生既事<br />\n都不可忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20dbe0e59cf06ff7f92e6c5b6b80800e7bd5e46f","tid":1351364,"uid":29461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:23:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"17354ddd8727895bdbee78c8a4d7d05d66259f27","tid":1351364,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:23:40.000Z","msg":"TVB除非由底改變 唔係一樣都係仆街"},{"pid":"f2ddd297d6483be350769814d51f347ecca23aee","tid":1351364,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d570cc5b6f223e0ed41a3f5ece40c55fc0dfc0b","tid":1351364,"uid":57,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:22:20.000Z","msg":"應該政府班高層喺今日記者會前都仲以為西環果邊嚴重過元朗，元朗果邊只係諗住用嚟分散注意力，冇諗過搞到對記者/普通人嚟講係咁嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開記者會前諗定哂點答中上環果邊點知全部都問元朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:23:46.000Z","msg":"用得老黑幫手做野<br />\n就應該要預計到佢地會有機會失控<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.g